        <updateDate>2021-12-10T15:23:03Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>HOPE for HOMES Act of 2021</b></p> <p> This bill provides support for energy efficiency upgrades in homes.</p> <p> Specifically, the bill directs the Department of Energy (DOE) to establish a grant program that supports training on how to efficiently retrofit homes. In addition, DOE must establish a Home Energy Savings Retrofit Rebate Program to provide rebates for homeowners to invest in energy efficiency improvements. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
